312
00:24:28,520 --> 00:24:30,370
We're not perfect.

313
00:24:31,690 --> 00:24:33,670
But in failing, we still learn.

314
00:24:34,110 --> 00:24:38,400
And when we learn, we get better for the next time.

315
00:24:41,470 --> 00:24:42,290
Just do it.

316
00:24:43,420 --> 00:24:44,120
Just do it.

317
00:24:45,270 --> 00:24:48,330
Whatever he's calling you to do, just do it.

318
00:24:49,280 --> 00:24:56,000
Don't let years go by like that prisoner in his own mind on a jungle somewhere in the South Pacific,

319
00:24:56,000 --> 00:24:58,540
